[LLM JUSTIFICATION]
This is a product_issue request about test availability and expiration. The customer is asking about how long tests stay active. Document 7 [7] directly addresses test expiration time and explains that tests can have defined start and end times that control when they remain active. The document explains the consequences when a test expires (candidates cannot access, invite button disabled, cannot invite new candidates). Document 1 [1] mentions archiving as an alternative to deletion if you want to retain a test but hide it. The customer's issue is likely related to test expiration settings rather than a bug or feature request. This can be resolved with status="replied" by explaining the test expiration feature and guiding them to check their test settings. No escalation is needed as this is a straightforward product question with clear documentation available.

